345
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:53,960
<font color="#FFFF00">(Pumuckl) Huibuh!</font>

346
00:22:54,40 --> 00:22:57,40
<font color="#FFFFFF">Also, wirklich alles in Ordnung?</font>

347
